        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3806994819" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13810759697109058755">I didn’t think I could love this book as much as I did the first one but I was wrong! These characters pull you in and you feel the weight of all of their emotions. Such a great story line while also bringing a joyous reminder that we’re all just characters in the Great Author’s own story. And what a privilege it is. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


